OL,3,CWoman 'imprisoned' in room for 15
OL,4,Cyears as mobility issues led to weight-
OL,5,Cgain
OL,7,FA disabled woman says she has been
OL,8,Fimprisoned in the kitchen in her home
OL,9,Ffor the past 15 years due to mobility
OL,10,Fissues.JIlla Smyth, from Gillingham,
OL,11,FKent, is unable to walk or climb the
OL,12,Fstairs in her house, after she has
OL,13,Flost her mobility, following arthritis
OL,14,Fand a number of falls and operations.
OL,16,FFor years, she has had to sleep, eat
OL,17,Fand use the toilet in the same 13ft
OL,18,Fsquare room as they cannot afford to
OL,19,Fadapt her house, or move to more
OL,20,Fsuitable accommodation.
