OL,3,CWoman 'imprisoned' in room for 15
OL,4,Cyears as mobility issues led to weight-
OL,5,Cgain
OL,7,FBeing stuck in one room led to her
OL,8,Fgaining weight, and now she is unable
OL,9,Fto leave because a wheelchair will not
OL,10,Ffit through their door or up the
OL,11,Fgarden steps.
OL,13,FMrs Smyth and her husband Alan are
OL,14,Fcalling for more help from Medway
OL,15,FCouncil to adapt their house to become
OL,16,Fwheelchair-friendly.
OL,18,FIlla Smyth said: "When you live in a
OL,19,Fhouse like this, you're just stuck in
OL,20,Fa box by yourself. People forget you.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
