OL,3,CWoman 'imprisoned' in room for 15
OL,4,Cyears as mobility issues led to weight-
OL,5,Cgain
OL,7,F"Every day. So if it wasn't for my
OL,8,Fhusband. I think I would've just died
OL,9,Fyears ago. Given up."
OL,11,FHer husband Alan has files full of
OL,12,Fletters he sent to Medway Council. He
OL,13,Fsays he first applied for a grant to
OL,14,Fadapt his house 10 years ago.
OL,16,FAlan Smyth said: "They have tried to
OL,17,Fbe seen to be doing the right thing
OL,18,Fwithout having any intention of doing
OL,19,Fanything.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
