OL,3,CWoman 'imprisoned' in room for 15
OL,4,Cyears as mobility issues led to weight-
OL,5,Cgain
OL,7,F"I've been fighting them for 10 years,
OL,8,Fand all I get is lies, after lies,
OL,9,Fafter lies."
OL,11,FMichael Erhardt, Disability Rights UK
OL,12,Fsaid: "I think it's important to
OL,13,Funderstand that this is a very common
OL,14,Fsituation for disabled people in the
OL,15,FUK... we all have a right to
OL,16,Faccessible housing that keeps us warm
OL,17,Fand safe.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
