OL,3,CWoman 'imprisoned' in room for 15
OL,4,Cyears as mobility issues led to weight-
OL,5,Cgain
OL,7,F"One of the key issues is that local
OL,8,Fauthorities are massively over-
OL,9,Fstretched. The problem, with the
OL,10,F(Disabled Facilities Grant) is that it
OL,11,Fis a very meagre amount of money.
OL,13,F"It's still set at #30,000, at a top
OL,14,Flevel, that a local authority can
OL,15,Fprovide, and has been so since around
OL,16,F2008.
OL,18,F"If you think about how much more
OL,19,Fthings cost now and how much less you
OL,20,Fcan get, you can see where some of the
OL,21,Fissues lie.
