OL,3,CWoman 'imprisoned' in room for 15
OL,4,Cyears as mobility issues led to weight-
OL,5,Cgain
OL,7,F"Councils have a duty of care to all
OL,8,Fpeople within its boundaries. Part of
OL,9,Fthat, under the Care Act 2014, is to
OL,10,Fmake sure that people's health doesn't
OL,11,Fget worse as a result of their
OL,12,Fcircumstances such as this."
OL,14,FHe advises if anyone is in a similar
OL,15,Fsituation people can receive help
OL,16,Fthrough the Law Centres Network,
OL,17,FShelter, Crisis, but also from local
OL,18,Fdisabled people's organisations.
