OL,4,Cyears as mobility issues led to weight-
OL,5,Cgain
OL,7,FMedway Council told ITV News Meridian:
OL,8,F"In November last year, a visit was
OL,9,Fconducted to assess the feasibility of
OL,10,Fhome improvements.
OL,12,F"It concluded the only feasible
OL,13,Fadaptation under the Disabled
OL,14,FFacilities Grant is the provision of
OL,15,Frear access.
OL,17,F"The works required to provide bathing
OL,18,Fand sleeping facilities were not
OL,19,Fconsidered to be reasonable and
OL,20,Fpracticable under the Disabled
OL,21,FFacilities Grant criteria.
