OL,3,CWoman 'imprisoned' in room for 15
OL,4,Cyears as mobility issues led to weight-
OL,5,Cgain
OL,7,F"Mr and Mrs Smyth have also been
OL,8,Fadvised of an alternative option - a
OL,9,FMoving Home Grant to assist with fees
OL,10,Fand costs relating to moving to a more
OL,11,Fsuitable property.
OL,13,F"A letter was sent to Mr and Mrs Smyth
OL,14,Fin March asking whether they wish to
OL,15,Fcontinue with an application for the
OL,16,Faccess works, and requesting benefit
OL,17,Finformation to confirm their
OL,18,Feligibility for the Disabled
OL,19,FFacilities Grant.
