OL,7,F"The council continues to keep the
OL,8,Fcase open while awaiting their
OL,9,Fresponse."
OL,11,FMr and Mrs Smyth say they could not
OL,12,Fapply for a grant to move to a more
OL,13,Fsuitable home, as there are no such
OL,14,Fhomes they can afford.
